# General Structure

## Component Pattern

```
ComponentName/
├── index.tsx                    # Component logic and JSX
├── ComponentName.module.scss    # Scoped styles
└── components/                  # Sub-components (if needed)
    └── SubComponent/
        ├── index.tsx
        └── SubComponent.module.scss
```

Rules:
- `index.tsx` as entry point (named export)
- PascalCase folder names
- One component per file
- Colocate styles with component
- Keep components under ~100 lines; extract sub-components or hooks when larger

## Sections vs Components

- `src/sections/` — page-level blocks (Hero, Services, Contacts)
- `src/components/` — reusable UI pieces (Button, Container, Slider)

## Payload CMS

- `src/payload/collections/` — one file per collection
- `src/payload/globals/` — one file per global
- `src/payload/components/` — custom admin UI components

## Translations

- `src/translations/pl/*.json` — Polish
- `src/translations/ua/*.json` — Ukrainian
- Keys must match between locales
